You are an expert in TypeScript, Vue 3, Nuxt 3, Pinia, Vue Router, VueUse, and Tailwind CSS.

# Project Type
This is a Nuxt 3 full-stack application using the Composition API, TypeScript, Pinia, and Tailwind CSS.

## Tech Stack
- Nuxt 3 (latest)
- Vue 3 Composition API
- TypeScript 5+
- Pinia for state management
- VueUse composables
- Tailwind CSS
- Nuxt UI or shadcn-vue
- Zod for validation

## Code Style and Structure

- Use `<script setup>` syntax for all components
- Use Composition API exclusively — no Options API
- Use TypeScript for all files
- Use `defineProps`, `defineEmits`, `defineExpose` with TypeScript
- Prefer composables over mixins
- Keep templates clean; extract complex logic to composables

## Nuxt 3 Auto-imports

```vue
<!-- Nuxt auto-imports: no need to manually import these -->
<!-- ref, computed, watch, onMounted — from Vue -->
<!-- useFetch, useAsyncData, navigateTo, useRoute — from Nuxt -->
<!-- All composables from ~/composables/ -->
<!-- All utils from ~/utils/ -->
```

## Component Patterns

```vue
<!-- components/UserCard.vue -->
<script setup lang="ts">
interface Props {
  user: User;
  showActions?: boolean;
}

interface Emits {
  (e: 'edit', userId: string): void;
  (e: 'delete', userId: string): void;
}

const props = withDefaults(defineProps<Props>(), {
  showActions: false,
});

const emit = defineEmits<Emits>();

const formattedDate = computed(() =>
  new Date(props.user.createdAt).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN')
);

function handleEdit() {
  emit('edit', props.user.id);
}
</script>

<template>
  <div class="rounded-lg border p-4">
    <h3 class="font-semibold">{{ user.name }}</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">{{ formattedDate }}</p>
    <div v-if="showActions" class="mt-2 flex gap-2">
      <button @click="handleEdit">编辑</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>
```

## Data Fetching Patterns

```typescript
// pages/users/index.vue
<script setup lang="ts">
// useFetch — 自动处理 SSR hydration
const { data: users, pending, error, refresh } = await useFetch<User[]>('/api/users', {
  key: 'users-list',
  transform: (data) => data.map(formatUser),
});

// useAsyncData — 更多控制
const { data: post } = await useAsyncData(
  `post-${route.params.id}`,
  () => $fetch(`/api/posts/${route.params.id}`),
  { watch: [() => route.params.id] }
);

// $fetch — 仅客户端事件触发的请求
async function submitForm(data: FormData) {
  try {
    await $fetch('/api/posts', { method: 'POST', body: data });
    await refresh();
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('[submitForm] 提交失败:', error);
  }
}
</script>
```

## Server API Routes (Nitro)

```typescript
// server/api/users/index.get.ts
import { z } from 'zod';

const QuerySchema = z.object({
  page: z.coerce.number().min(1).default(1),
  limit: z.coerce.number().min(1).max(100).default(20),
});

export default defineEventHandler(async (event) => {
  const query = await getValidatedQuery(event, QuerySchema.parse);
  const users = await usersService.list(query);
  return users;
});

// server/api/users/[id].get.ts
export default defineEventHandler(async (event) => {
  const id = getRouterParam(event, 'id');
  if (!id) {
    throw createError({ statusCode: 400, statusMessage: '缺少用户 ID' });
  }
  const user = await usersService.findById(id);
  if (!user) {
    throw createError({ statusCode: 404, statusMessage: '用户不存在' });
  }
  return user;
});

// server/api/users/index.post.ts
import { z } from 'zod';
const CreateUserSchema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1),
  email: z.string().email(),
});

export default defineEventHandler(async (event) => {
  const body = await readValidatedBody(event, CreateUserSchema.parse);
  const user = await usersService.create(body);
  setResponseStatus(event, 201);
  return user;
});
```

## Pinia Store Patterns

```typescript
// stores/useAuthStore.ts
import { defineStore } from 'pinia';

interface User {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  email: string;
}

export const useAuthStore = defineStore('auth', () => {
  // State
  const user = ref<User | null>(null);
  const token = ref<string | null>(null);

  // Getters
  const isAuthenticated = computed(() => !!user.value && !!token.value);
  const displayName = computed(() => user.value?.name ?? '游客');

  // Actions
  async function login(credentials: LoginCredentials) {
    const response = await $fetch<{ user: User; token: string }>('/api/auth/login', {
      method: 'POST',
      body: credentials,
    });
    user.value = response.user;
    token.value = response.token;
  }

  function logout() {
    user.value = null;
    token.value = null;
    navigateTo('/login');
  }

  return { user, token, isAuthenticated, displayName, login, logout };
}, {
  persist: {
    storage: persistedState.localStorage,
    paths: ['user', 'token'],
  },
});
```

## Composables

```typescript
// composables/useUsers.ts
export function useUsers() {
  const { data: users, pending: isLoading, error, refresh } = useFetch<User[]>('/api/users');

  const activeUsers = computed(() =>
    users.value?.filter(u => u.isActive) ?? []
  );

  async function createUser(data: CreateUserInput) {
    await $fetch('/api/users', { method: 'POST', body: data });
    await refresh();
  }

  async function deleteUser(id: string) {
    await $fetch(`/api/users/${id}`, { method: 'DELETE' });
    await refresh();
  }

  return { users, activeUsers, isLoading, error, createUser, deleteUser };
}
```

## Nuxt Configuration

```typescript
// nuxt.config.ts
export default defineNuxtConfig({
  modules: [
    '@nuxtjs/tailwindcss',
    '@pinia/nuxt',
    '@vueuse/nuxt',
    'nuxt-ui',
  ],
  runtimeConfig: {
    // Server-only (private)
    databaseUrl: '',
    secretKey: '',
    // Public (exposed to client)
    public: {
      apiBase: 'http://localhost:3000',
    },
  },
  typescript: {
    strict: true,
  },
});
```

## Error Handling Patterns

```typescript
// 全局错误处理
export default defineNuxtPlugin((nuxtApp) => {
  nuxtApp.vueApp.config.errorHandler = (error, context) => {
    console.error('[Global Error]', error, context);
  };
});

// 组件中的错误处理
const error = useError();

// API 路由错误处理
export default defineEventHandler(async (event) => {
  try {
    return await processRequest(event);
  } catch (err) {
    if (err instanceof ValidationError) {
      throw createError({ statusCode: 422, data: err.details });
    }
    throw createError({ statusCode: 500, statusMessage: '服务器内部错误' });
  }
});
```

## File Naming Conventions

- Components: `PascalCase.vue`
- Pages: `kebab-case.vue` (e.g., `user-profile.vue`)
- Composables: `use[Name].ts`
- Stores: `use[Name]Store.ts`
- Server routes: `[resource]/index.[method].ts`
- Middleware: `[name].ts` or `[name].global.ts`

## What Cursor Should Do

- Use `<script setup>` syntax always
- Auto-import Vue and Nuxt composables (no manual imports needed)
- Use Composition API with TypeScript generics
- Suggest `useFetch` for SSR-compatible data fetching
- Generate Pinia stores using the Setup Store pattern
- Suggest proper server route file naming ([id].get.ts, index.post.ts)
- Recommend `getValidatedQuery` and `readValidatedBody` for input validation

## What Cursor Should Avoid

- Do NOT use Options API
- Do NOT manually import auto-imported composables
- Do NOT use Vuex (use Pinia instead)
- Do NOT use `axios` in Nuxt (use `$fetch` or `useFetch`)
- Do NOT mix SSR and client-only code without proper guards
- Do NOT use `process.env` directly in Nuxt — use `useRuntimeConfig()`
- Do NOT skip error handling in server routes
